  "ai_usage": "A ready 'featured plan' card. The gradient edge uses background: solid padding-box, gradient border-box with a transparent border. On hover/focus-within it lifts (translateY) and deepens its colored glow. The CTA is a ghost button that fills on hover. For a full pricing section, render three of these and only give the middle one the gradient border + glow to mark it as recommended.",
  "path": "effects/combos-recipes/pricing-card.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Pricing Card (composed)</title>\n  <script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n  {\n    \"id\": \"pricing-card\",\n    \"title\": \"Pricing Card (composed)\",\n    \"summary\": \"A 'featured' pricing card combining a gradient border, hover lift, colored glow, and a fill-sweep button.\",\n    \"description\": \"Composes gradient-border + card-lift + glow-shadow + fill-sweep-button into a polished, highlight-worthy pricing tier card.\",\n    \"theme\": \"combos-recipes\",\n    \"categories\": [\"recipe\", \"pricing\", \"card\"],\n    \"tags\": [\"pricing\", \"card\", \"gradient-border\", \"lift\", \"glow\", \"cta\", \"composition\"],\n    \"tech\": [\"css\"],\n    \"era\": \"2020s\",\n    \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n    \"dependencies\": [],\n    \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (uses the padding-box/border-box gradient-border trick).\",\n    \"performance_notes\": \"Static gradient border + transform/shadow on hover. Cheap.\",\n    \"accessibility_notes\": \"Real list + button with focus ring. Hover lift also triggers on :focus-within. Contrast preserved.\",\n    \"customization\": [\n      { \"name\": \"--accent / --accent-2\", \"description\": \"Brand gradient\", \"default\": \"#7c5cff / #2dd4bf\" },\n      { \"name\": \"content\", \"description\": \"Plan name, price, features\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n    ],\n    \"variations\": [\"Three-up pricing row with the middle one featured\", \"Monthly/annual toggle\", \"Add a 'Most popular' ribbon\"],\n    \"related\": [\"gradient-border\", \"card-lift\", \"glow-shadow\", \"fill-sweep-button\"],\n    \"ai_usage\": \"A ready 'featured plan' card. The gradient edge uses background: solid padding-box, gradient border-box with a transparent border. On hover/focus-within it lifts (translateY) and deepens its colored glow. The CTA is a ghost button that fills on hover. For a full pricing section, render three of these and only give the middle one the gradient border + glow to mark it as recommended.\"\n  }\n  </script>\n  <style>\n    :root { --accent: #7c5cff; --accent-2: #2dd4bf; --bg: #11141c; }\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body { height: 100%; margin: 0; }\n    body { display: grid; place-items: center; background: #0b0d12; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; padding: 1rem; }\n    .price-card {\n      width: 300px; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 20px; color: #e7ebf3;\n      border: 2px solid transparent;\n      background: linear-gradient(var(--bg), var(--bg)) padding-box,\n                  linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2)) border-box;\n      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(124,92,255,.18);\n      transition: transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;\n    }\n    .price-card:hover, .price-card:focus-within {\n      transform: translateY(-8px);\n      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 45%, transparent);\n    }\n    .badge { display: inline-block; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase;\n      color: #fff; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2)); padding: .25rem .6rem; border-radius: 999px; }\n    .price { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; margin: .8rem 0 0; }\n    .price small { font-size: 1rem; color: #8b93a7; font-weight: 500; }\n    ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1.2rem 0; }\n    li { padding: .4rem 0; color: #b7bdcc; } li::before { content: \"✓ \"; color: var(--accent-2); font-weight: 800; }\n    .buy {\n      position: relative; overflow: hidden; width: 100%; cursor: pointer; isolation: isolate;\n      background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--accent); color: #fff;\n      padding: .8rem; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; transition: color .3s;\n    }\n    .buy::before { content: \"\"; position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: -1; transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2)); transition: transform .3s; }\n    .buy:hover::before, .buy:focus-visible::before { transform: scaleX(1); }\n    .buy:focus-visible { outline: 3px solid #fff; outline-offset: 2px; }\n    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .price-card, .buy, .buy::before { transition: none; } }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <article class=\"price-card\">\n    <span class=\"badge\">Most popular</span>\n    <p class=\"price\">$29<small>/mo</small></p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Unlimited projects</li>\n      <li>Priority support</li>\n      <li>Advanced analytics</li>\n      <li>Team collaboration</li>\n    </ul>\n    <button class=\"buy\">Choose Pro</button>\n  </article>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
